OL,3,CProgramme listings for SUN 8 MAR
OL,4,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GThis episode meets people who've
OL,6,     Gtaken big risks and explores how
OL,7,     Git's affected their lives.
OL,8,     GMotorbikers James and Peter are
OL,9,     Gboth rushed in. Ex-miner Alfred
OL,10,     Ghas severe chest pain.
OL,11,G2305F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GKeith is rushed to Queen's after
OL,13,     Ga cardiac arrest. Joanna has a
OL,14,     Gspinal fracture after falling off
OL,15,     Ga horse. And 79-year-old John has
OL,16,     Gbeen run over by a car while out
OL,17,     Gshopping.
