OL,4,G0005F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GParamedics treat a woman with a
OL,6,     Gpossible bleed on the brain, a
OL,7,     Gbaby whose heart is beating
OL,8,     Gextremely fast, a man showing
OL,9,     Gsigns of a stroke, and a woman
OL,10,     Gwho may have sepsis.
